    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and honestly, she still looks and smells like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s a total time capsule\u2014not a speck of dust in the engine bay and the paint has that deep, glass-like shine you usually only see in museums. I\u2019ve always kept her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, only bringing her out for those perfect sunny afternoon cruises. She drives like a dream, smooth as silk and ready for a new home where she\u2019ll be just as cherished. If you\u2019re looking for the best of the best, you\u2019ve found it. Come by, let's have a chat, and see her for yourself!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a superlative example of the platform, curated for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection. The powerplant retains its factory-spec compression ratios, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear torque curve that pulls relentlessly to redline. I have ensured the drivetrain remains tight, with zero lash in the differential and a gearbox that clicks into gear with bolt-action precision. The chassis has been preserved to maintain its original torsional rigidity, ensuring the suspension geometry remains uncompromised under high lateral G-loads. Every bushing is compliant, the cooling system has been pressurized and verified, and the electrical loom is free of parasitic draws. This is a turn-key machine optimized for peak kinetic output.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
