    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive poetry. This isn't merely a vehicle; it is a preserved moment in time, finished in a deep, lustrous hue that catches the twilight like a secret. The engine doesn't just run\u2014it breathes with a rhythmic, soulful purr that promises endless horizons. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of pristine materials, smelling faintly of rich heritage and expensive memories. Every stitch and every chrome accent reflects a life of pampered devotion, offering a driving experience that feels less like travel and more like a return to a golden age of craftsmanship. To own this is to curate a legend.",
